## 3ct Lab-Grown: The $42,980 Savings Argument

The lab arbitrage at 3ct is the most financially significant buying decision in the engagement ring market. An IGI 3ct E-VVS1 lab-grown costs $5,800 (ID [28944023](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28944023?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)). The natural G-VS2 equivalent costs $48,780. That is $42,980 in savings for an identical 9.4mm stone. Even accounting for lab's lower resale (10–20% vs natural's 40–50%), the financial case for lab at 3ct is overwhelming.

